[4.40415, "o", "- Batch movement commands (separated by '\"'\"'&'\"'\"', no restriction on the number of commands): e.g., `move N & E`, `move S & S & W`, `move N & E & S & W`, `move N & N & N & N & N & N`.\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
